<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.178.64426.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. LM (A, B) and SEM (C-H) images of species found in the transitional zone at Mykolaiv city: A Aulacoseira islandica, valve view B Aulacoseira nivalis, valve view C Aulacoseira subarctica, girdle view of complete frustule D-H Actinocyclus normanii valve view (D pseudonodulus shown with arrow, E, G) and girdle view (H, F). Scale bars: 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/545735" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

